### CampusConnect API Tests

@nestjs_url = http://localhost:3000
@go_url = http://localhost:8080
@api_key = secure_api_key_123

### 1. User CRUD - Create User
# @name registerUser
POST {{nestjs_url}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@student.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "name": "Test Student"
}

### 2. User CRUD - Login
# @name loginUser
POST {{nestjs_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@student.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### 3. Event CRUD - Create Event
# @name createEvent
POST {{nestjs_url}}/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Spring Hackathon 2024",
  "description": "Tech event for students.",
  "date": "2024-05-20T10:00:00Z",
  "location": "Istanbul",
  "category": "Technology"
}

### 4. Event CRUD - Get Events (Pagination & Filters)
GET {{nestjs_url}}/events?page=1&limit=10&location=Istanbul&category=Technology

### 5. Event Participation - Join Event via GraphQL
# @name joinEvent
POST {{nestjs_url}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "query": "mutation { joinEvent(eventId: 1) { id eventId userId } }"
}

### 6. Event Participation - Leave Event via GraphQL
# @name leaveEvent
POST {{nestjs_url}}/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "query": "mutation { leaveEvent(eventId: 1) }"
}

### 7. Fetch Analytics via Go Service (Top Events)
GET {{go_url}}/analytics/top-events
x-api-key: {{api_key}}

### 8. Fetch Analytics via Go Service (Weekly Participation Stats)
GET {{go_url}}/analytics/stats
x-api-key: {{api_key}}

### 9. Test Rate Limiting on Go Service (Requires sending > 60 requests/min)
# Will return RFC 7807 problem details
GET {{go_url}}/analytics/top-events
x-api-key: {{api_key}}
